1. Concentric beak sculpture;
2. Orange foot, when alive;
3. Narrow, anterior/more central umbo.

1. Triangular;
2. Steep posterior ridge;
3. Distinct chevron markings.

1. Thin shell;
2. Lateral teeth thin and delicate;
3. Rays;
4. Posteriorly iridescent nacre.
